This is the INSTALL file for CHOICE
____________________________________________________________________

To compile:

** You will need Borland C 3.1 (should compile under TurboC as well)
and the "Cats" library.  You can download the "Cats" library from
http://www.freedos.org/jhall/cats/



1. type:

   MAKE -F MAKEFILE.BC

2. the resulting program is CHOICE.EXE

3. enjoy!
